01:03:23.270 --> 01:03:26.660
Today is my wife's birthday. I picked one for you also.

01:03:26.660 --> 01:03:28.990
<i>What am I to you?</i>

01:03:32.500 --> 01:03:34.750
Just because you blocked the contact, do you think I can't find you?

01:03:34.750 --> 01:03:38.190
<i>This will end only if I die, right? Then I'll die.</i>

01:03:41.390 --> 01:03:43.610
<i>Who are you?</i>

01:03:43.610 --> 01:03:46.120
I am this person's sister.

01:03:49.340 --> 01:03:52.220
<i>How is Myung Seop these days?</i>

01:03:52.220 --> 01:03:57.310
<i>I think my bracelet and your necklace are from the same set.</i>

01:03:57.310 --> 01:04:00.620
<i>Can I ask where you bought this from?</i>

01:04:00.620 --> 01:04:03.200
<i>Where did you buy it from?</i>

